{
  "stem": "25598.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I think the only way I could use my mind-- or maybe these were like stepping stones to sanity, to-- to-- my way of running away temporarily from the reality that I was in and going-- going back home where I find myself in shul and we're running around and the men are shouting, quiet, quiet, it's davening, you know.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then all these things used to come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- well, that's how we lived for-- for three and 1/2 years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the war turned, and then we knew that the withdrawing SS troops slaughter everybody they find alive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So people started to dig holes under the huts and cover them with camouflaged boards or with what have you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But these were literally holes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't like a cellar or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was a hole in the ground where we were planning to hide when-- when the Germans withdraw.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we knew when they withdrew from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if everybody else knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we-- we were in the hut there, in the-- in the hole.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I mean, even getting down there, was-- it was such a narrow hole to get down there that you could hardly sort of slide through it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and down there it was dark and it was wet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the baby was crying and people were moaning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was like living in a hole in the ground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I'm not even sure that it was-- if it was a few days or if it was a few hours.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember that, suddenly, we heard Russian songs.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
